@{b}Synopsis:@{ub} @{b}sign(value)@{ub} 

@{b}Function:@{ub} Checks the sign of a number 

@{b}Arguments:@{ub} @{b}value@{ub} - a number 

@{b}Result:@{ub} -1 if @{b}value@{ub} is negative, 1 if positive, 0 if zero 


@endnode 
@node func_sin "sin()" 
@toc FuncRef

@{b}@{u}sin()@{ub}@{uu}


