@{b}Results:@{ub} None. 


@endnode 


@node rxrevealproject "RevealProject" 
@toc ARexxFuncInd

@{b}@{u}RevealProject@{ub}@{uu}


@{b}Name:@{ub} @{b}RevealProject@{ub} -- Reveal a hidden project 

@{b}Synopsis:@{ub} @{b}RevealProject Project/K@{ub} 
   @{b}RC@{ub} = @{i}Success@{ui} 

@{b}Function:@{ub} Open all windows of a hidden Fiasco project. This project will 
