@{b}@{u}Save@{ub}@{uu}


@{b}Name:@{ub} @{b}Save@{ub} -- Save a Fiasco database 

@{b}Synopsis:@{ub} @{b}Save@{ub} 
   @{b}RC@{ub} = @{i}Success@{ui} 

@{b}Function:@{ub} Saves the addressed Fiasco database under the old name on disk. 

@{b}Arguments:@{ub} none. 

@{b}Results:@{ub} @{b}RC@{ub} - Success. 


