@node rxsort "Sort" 
@toc ARexxFuncInd

@{b}@{u}Sort@{ub}@{uu}


@{b}Name:@{ub} @{b}Sort@{ub} -- Sort a database 

@{b}Synopsis:@{ub} @{b}Sort Fields/A/M,Descending/S,Index/K@{ub}
   @{b}RC@{ub} = @{i}Success@{ui} 

@{b}Function:@{ub} Creates an sorted index for the addressed database according to 
   the alphabetical or equivalent priority of the contents of the 
   specified fields.  This command may be only called in record mode.  

