@{b}@{u}UnlockGUI@{ub}@{uu}


@{b}Name:@{ub} @{b}UnlockGUI@{ub} - Unlock Fiasco's GUI 

@{b}Synopsis:@{ub} @{b}UnlockGUI@{ub}
   @{b}RC@{ub} = @{i}Success@{ui} 

