@node AUTHOR "Support for Fiasco" 
@toc main

@{b}@{u}Support for Fiasco@{ub}@{uu}


@{b}Updates@{ub}

New versions of Fiasco will be uploaded to Aminet first. They should be 
available in the directory @{b}biz/dbase@{ub}. For more information about Aminet, 
send an eMail with the word @{b}Help@{ub} in the mail body to 
@{b}Aminet-Server\@aminet.org@{ub}. 

@{b}Mailing List@{ub}

To subscribe to the Fiasco mailing list, send a mail with the text 
@{b}subscribe fiasco@{ub} in the @{i}mail body@{ui} to @{b}majordomo\@in-tec.de@{ub}. To write 
messages into the list, write to @{b}fiasco\@amigaworld.com@{ub}. 

    If you have problems while subscribing to the mailing list, you may 
try to subscribe to the backup mailing list. This mailing list will be 
used in the case when the normal mailing list is be down. Send a mail 
with the @{i}subject@{ui} @{b}subscribe fiasco@{ub} to @{b}listserv\@wanderer.gun.de@{ub} . Please 
also read the introduction mail from the mailing list.  


@{b}Word Wide Web@{ub}

There is also an internet homepage for Fiasco. You may obtain the latest 
news about Fiasco there. The URL is 
@{b}http://www.amigaworld.com/support/fiasco/@{ub}. 


@{b}Author@{ub}

The author of Fiasco can be reached at the following addresses:
Nils Bandener
Uhlenbruch 30
D-33098 Paderborn
Germany

